ZH: 我很累，然而我还是要继续工作。
EN: I am tired, however I still have to continue working.

ZH: 他很聪明，然而他却不努力学习。
EN: He is smart, however he doesn't work hard.

ZH: 这个项目看起来很简单，然而却需要很长的时间来完成。
EN: This project seems easy, however it requires a long time to complete.

ZH: 我们原本计划去旅行，然而因为天气不好而取消了。
EN: We planned to go on a trip, however it got cancelled due to bad weather.

ZH: 这家餐厅的装修很好看，然而菜品却没有什么特色。
EN: The decoration of this restaurant is nice, however the dishes are not special.

ZH: 她的声音很美，然而她却不喜欢唱歌。
EN: Her voice is beautiful, however she doesn't like to sing.

ZH: 我们的想法不同，然而我们仍然是好朋友。
EN: Our ideas are different, however we are still good friends.

ZH: 这个产品设计独特，然而价格却很昂贵。
EN: This product has a unique design, however the price is very expensive.

ZH: 虽然他很瘦，然而他的食量却非常大。
EN: Although he is skinny, his appetite is very big.

ZH: 这个城市的空气质量很差，然而很多人仍然选择在这里生活。
EN: The air quality of this city is poor, however many people still choose to live here.

ZH: 这部电影票房很高，然而评价却不太好。
EN: This movie has a high box office, however the reviews are not very good.

ZH: 这个故事开始很慢，然而后面的情节却非常精彩。
EN: This story starts slowly, however the later plot is very exciting.

ZH: 这个学生很聪明，然而缺乏自信。
EN: This student is smart, however lacks confidence.

ZH: 每天他都很努力学习，然而成绩却一直没有提高。
EN: He studies hard every day, however his grades have not improved.

ZH: 虽然下雨了，然而他还是决定去跑步。
EN: Although it is raining, he still decides to go for a run.

ZH: 她试了很多办法，然而问题依然没有解决。
EN: She tried many methods, however the problem still hasn't been solved.

ZH: 这本小说的结局很意外，然而很有吸引力。
EN: The ending of this novel is unexpected, however very appealing.

ZH: 虽然失望了，然而我们不能放弃。
EN: Although disappointed, we cannot give up.

ZH: 虽然很晚了，然而我们的工作还没有完成。
EN: Although it is late, our work is not yet finished.

ZH: 这个人虽然年纪小，然而智慧却超过了同龄人。
EN: Although young, this person's wisdom surpasses peers.
